Class ObjectPropertyCommand

java.lang.Object
  PopupPanel
      liber.browse.client.InputPopupPanel
          liber.browse.client.ObjectPropertyCommand

public class ObjectPropertyCommand
extends InputPopupPanel

ObjectPropertyCommmand is initialised when a user selects an object property and elicits which or what type of objects are in the range of the property.

Version:
1.1 December 2007, 1.2 March 2008, 1.3 May 2008, 1.4 January 2009
